https://github.com/nrkn/SimpleRL

By Nik Coughlin

OK this was fun to do :)

I wrote this using the Dartmouth BASIC 4th Edition (1968) specs and then tested
it with QB and GW Basic. It works in those and as far as I can tell it should 
run on pretty much any simple BASIC.

I tried to keep it idiomatic but it could probably be improved a lot.